;;; ‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî‚Äî
(defun gravitate-toward (goal num delta)
  "Either add to a number, or subtract from it; whichever brings it closer to zero.
In addition, the resultant value shall not ‚Äúpass‚Äù zero."
  (cond
    ((< num goal)
     (‚Ä¶:at-most goal (+ num delta)))
    ((> num goal)
     (‚Ä¶:at-least goal (- num delta)))
    ('t
     goal)))


